th=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077670/extras/4893b8eda6fe0a770cad5a4e737a7ad8.webm?t=1765825394\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077670/extras/4893b8eda6fe0a770cad5a4e737a7ad8.mp4?t=1765825394\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Be Careful:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You never know what might be waiting for you around the corner.</p>",
